<i>But I'm...</i>

20:02.930 --> 20:05.220
<i>all right now!</i>

20:06.430 --> 20:07.850
<i>Mist Breathing...</i>

20:08.180 --> 20:09.310
<i>Fifth Form...</i>

20:10.930 --> 20:12.690
<i>Sea of Clouds and Haze!</i>

20:17.770 --> 20:20.280
Well, that was some rapid-fire chopping,

20:20.280 --> 20:23.950
