20:26.240 --> 20:27.370
What?

20:27.990 --> 20:30.750
It looks like your senses
have totally dulled.

20:30.750 --> 20:33.080
It's because you've lived
for hundreds of years.

20:35.750 --> 20:37.540
I'm going to slash you next time.

20:37.540 --> 20:41.880
I have better things to do
than playing your stupid vase game all day.

20:43.090 --> 20:46.090
Don't underestimate me, you brat!

20:52.520 --> 20:54.230
DESTROY

20:54.230 --> 20:55.520
<i>Muichiro...</i>
DESTROY

20:57.060 --> 21:00.070
<i>Sorry I couldn't be more gentle with you.</i>

21:01.780 --> 21:03.190
<i>I could just never...</i>

21:03.190 --> 21:05.280
<i>afford to be that way.</i>

21:06.320 --> 21:08.410
<i>Being kind to others...</i>

21:09.370 --> 21:12.410
<i>is one more thing
that only the chosen ones can do.</i>

21:13.450 --> 21:14.580
<i>But...</i>

21:14.580 --> 21:16.170
<i>Muichiro...</i>

21:16.920 --> 21:19.380
<i>no matter how virtuous
a life you may lead,</i>

21:19.840 --> 21:24.630
<i>neither the gods nor Buddha
will protect you in the end.</i>

21:24.630 --> 21:27.890
<i>That's why I thought
I had to protect you.</i>

21:28.640 --> 21:29.850
<i>Muichiro...</i>

21:30.260 --> 21:33.020
<i>You're not like me.</i>

21:35.520 --> 21:38.190
<i>For the sake of someone
other than yourself...</i>

21:40.150 --> 21:41.820
<i>you can exert infinite strength.</i>

21:47.740 --> 21:50.120
